        <section class="small">
          <div class="small__image-block">
            <div class="small__image absolute-image">
              <picture>
                <source
                  media="(min-width: 470px)"
                  data-srcset="/assets/theme/build/img/bedrooms/bedrooms-3.jpg 1x, /assets/theme/build/img/bedrooms/bedrooms-3@2x.jpg 2x"
                  srcset="
                    /assets/theme/build/img/bedrooms/bedrooms-3.jpg    1x,
                    /assets/theme/build/img/bedrooms/bedrooms-3@2x.jpg 2x
                  "
                  width="1920"
                  height="720"
                />
                <img
                  loading="lazy"
                  class="lazyloaded"
                  src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAgADAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAACAAMAAAICjF8AOw=="
                  data-srcset="/assets/theme/build/img/bedrooms/bedrooms-3-mobile.jpg    1x, /assets/theme/build/img/bedrooms/bedrooms-3-mobile@2x.jpg 2x"
                  alt="Bedroom"
                  width="480"
                  height="720"
                  srcset="
                    /assets/theme/build/img/bedrooms/bedrooms-3-mobile.jpg    1x,
                    /assets/theme/build/img/bedrooms/bedrooms-3-mobile@2x.jpg 2x
                  "
                />
              </picture>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="small__text-block">
            <h2 class="small__title">
              Small spaces demand efficient storage solutions too
            </h2>
            <p class="small__text">
              A bespoke fitted wardrobe is not just for large bedrooms, small
              spaces require efficient design to make the most of the space, a
              made to measure wardrobe delivers just that and can provide twice
              as much storage than a free-standing wardrobe.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="small__button-block">
            <a href="book-app" class="button button_long _popup-link">
              BOOK APPOINTMENT
